					<p class="text-lg text-zinc-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">React Native apps often suffer from frame drops when processing heavy logic. Web Workers solve this by moving the work elsewhere.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
					
                    <!-- Large card: Isomorphic Code (Full Width) -->
