						<div class="flex-1 relative z-10">
							<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Isomorphic by design</h3>
							<p class="text-zinc-400 mb-8 max-w-md text-base leading-relaxed">
								Write your background logic once and run it everywhere. The same `Worker` API works on React Native (iOS/Android) and the browser.
							</p>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-zinc-500 text-sm font-mono">
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
